).

Structure. Flagellum with 20–23 flagellomeres (respectively 7%, 45%, 42% and 5% of 
40 specimens
) and flagellomeres narrow in apical 0.5. Height of eye 1.00–1.11 times as long as minimum distance between inner eye margins. Otherwise structure and sculpture as in female.
